com.inqwell.any

Class AnyMap

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.inqwell.any.AbstractComposite
      • com.inqwell.any.AbstractMap
        • com.inqwell.any.PropertyAccessMap
          • com.inqwell.any.AnyMap
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Any, Composite, Map, Serializable, Cloneable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    AnyOrderedMap, AnyPMap, CacheMap, ClientObject, KeyMap, ManagedObject, MultiHierarchyMap, SimpleMap, SoftCacheMap, UIDefaultsMap, WeakMap

    public abstract class AnyMap
extends PropertyAccessMap
implements Map, Cloneable
    AnyMap is a general collection class mapping keys of type Any to values of type Any. It is an abstract class providing an in-memory map implementation acting as a basis for concrete implementations.
